For each bid:

System generates:

* Score summary
* Individual evaluator comments
* Consensus explanation
* Final ranking rationale
* Compliance confirmation

This becomes the official evaluation report.

---

# 1️⃣5️⃣ BIAS and MANIPULATION PREVENTION CONTROLS

System prevents:

❌ Changing weights after opening
❌ Editing scores without trace
❌ Viewing financial bids early
❌ Evaluator seeing supplier identity (if blind mode enabled)
❌ Single-person award authority

Optional blind evaluation:

* Supplier identity hidden during technical scoring.

